===Noun===
'''snow''' {{uncountable}} - ''unless specified''

#The frozen, [[crystalline]] state of [[water]] that falls as [[precipitation]].
#A name for a [[shade]] of the [[colour]] [[white]].
#:<table><tr><td>snow colour: &nbsp;</td><td bgcolor="#F9F5E6" width="80">&nbsp; </td></tr></table>
#[[Random]] [[electrical]] [[noise]] in a [[television]] [[picture]].
#{{slang}} [[Cocaine]].
#{{countable}} A [[snowfall]]; a [[blanket]] of snow (''the frozen state of water'').
#:''We have had several heavy snows this year.''

